SUMMARY:Swap & Play! by Papillon Collective
DESCRIPTION:Our Swap & Play event by Papillon Collective is back just in time for spring cleaning! \nWe buy a lot of stuff for our babies. And then they grow. Really fast!  \nDonate your gentle used items to the pile while scoring some ‘new’ items for your growing baby. Then stay for the play!  \nItems we are accepting: Gently used (no stains\, rips\, etc.) – maternity clothing\, baby toys\, clothing\, opened packages of diapers\, baby wearing items\, misc newborn items\, toddler clothing up to 3 years old. \nEven if you don’t have any items to donate\, please come join us to play and socialize with other families. \nWe’ll have light refreshments\, toys to play with\, music\, and activities for all ages.  \nRAFFLE! We will have amazing prizes for you to win; sleep consultant sessions\, pelvic floor session\, massage\, and much more! \n$5 admissions will go to support putting on this event and expenses associated. \nAll unclaimed items will be donated to Mother + Child.  \nAny questions\, email caitlin@papillon-collective.com  \nWe look forward to seeing you! \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/swap-play-by-papillon-collective/
LOCATION:The Laurelhurst Club\, 3721 SE Ankeny St\, Portland\, OR\, 97214\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,Indoor,Kids Calendar,Playgroup
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Swap-Banner-980-x-552-px.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Papillon Collective":MAILTO:caitlin@papillon-collective.com
END:VEVENT
