SUMMARY:Sunday Family Movies at Ponzi Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:You asked. We’re extending it. 🍿 \nOur Sunday Family Movie Series rolls right into March at Ponzi — more cozy afternoons\, more popcorn\, more mac and cheese\, more reasons to gather. \nMarch 1 – The Goonies\nWe’re kicking off the month with The Goonies\, filmed in Astoria\, to celebrate our Oregon Coast Collection. Adventure\, nostalgia\, and a little Oregon pride. \nMarch 8 – Despicable Me\nWe’re launching our new Sunday brunch series alongside Despicable Me. Minions for the kids\, Dungeness crab Benedicts and Brut Rosé for the grown-ups. \nMarch 15 – Matilda the Musical\nSing along to Roald Dahl’s Matilda the Musical — bold\, brilliant\, and perfect for all ages. \nMarch 22 – The Sandlot\n“You’re killin’ me\, Smalls.” ⚾ We’re showing The Sandlot in celebration of MLB Opening Week — a spring classic about baseball and friendship. \nMarch 29 – Rookie of the Year\nWe’re closing out March with Rookie of the Year — because nothing pairs with early baseball season like a feel-good underdog story. \nSame cozy Sundays.\nNow through March.\nSee you at Ponzi. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/sunday-family-movies-at-ponzi-vineyards/2026-03-15/
LOCATION:Ponzi Vineyards\, 19500 SW MOUNTAIN HOME RD\, SHERWOOD\, OR\, 97140\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,Kids Calendar,Movie
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Tasting-room-terrace-1-1-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Ponzi Vineyards":MAILTO:marketing@ponzivineyards.com
END:VEVENT
