SUMMARY:Reptiles at The Portland Aquarium
DESCRIPTION:Come hang with reptiles at the Portland Aquarium!! We’re teaming up with PDX Critters to bring you an up-close\, hands-on experience you won’t forget. \nGet ready to meet incredible lizards\, snakes\, spiders\, and more — and yes\, you’ll even have the chance to hold some of these amazing animals! Whether you’re fascinated by scaly superstars\, curious about eight-legged friends\, or just want to conquer a fear in a safe and welcoming space\, this event is perfect for all ages. \nOur expert handlers will be sharing fun facts\, answering questions\, and teaching you all about: \n✨ Unique reptile adaptations \n✨ How these animals survive in the wild \n✨ Why reptiles and arachnids are so important to our ecosystems \n✨ How to safely and respectfully interact with them \nIt’s interactive\, educational\, and just the right amount of wild. \nBring your friends\, bring your family\, and come discover why reptiles rule the animal kingdom. 🐍💚 \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/reptiles-at-the-portland-aquarium-2/2026-03-15/
LOCATION:The Portland Aquarium\, 603 SW Broadway\, Portland\, OR\, 97205\, United States
CATEGORIES:Animals,Educational,Family Fun,Kids Calendar,STEM
